        "max_width": 520,
        "line_height": 14,
        "font_size": 10,
        "labels": {
          "greeting": "Hi {first_name},",
          "gift_greeting": "Hi {first_name},",
          "message": "Message",
          "recommendation": "PS:"
        },
        "generic_message_normal": "Thanks for your order.\nWe are here to make your life easier, so here are some ways we can help you further...\n• EASY GIFTING: delivered FREE next business day\n• EASY FUNDRAISING: got a school / club / charity you need to raise funds for?\n• EASY CATERING: from our Nedlands store\n\nEnjoy your meals, and make life a little easier with some quick wins in the kitchen by cooking all our products straight from frozen!!\n\nNathan & the team from Tommy Sugo",
